    <comment>- Update to 1.1.0:
  ## New Features
  - Adding new plotting functionality to plot_ridge by
  - Add plot_loo_interval
  - Add set_x_scale
  - Add new uniformity test
  - plot_compare: Default to plot ELPD differences
  ## Maintenance and bug fixes
  - Move ess evolution helper
  - Special handling of single plot figure in none backend
  - Add hypothesis test for plot_compare
  - Fix [tool.pytest] -&gt; [tool.pytest.ini_options] in pyproject.toml
  - Fix rootogram coords issue
  - Fix xlabel plot_loo_pit when coverage True
  - Use new validators
  - Fix plot_compare when relative_scale is true
  - Update dataset construction
  - Refactor plot_ppc_pit
  - ecdf_pit: fix colors and p_value_text
  - Handle mixed dims and MultiIndex warnings
  - misc bugs
  - Add tests for combine_plots
  ## Documentation
  - Format bare URL in README
  - Sort glossary alphabetically
  - Configure docstub and add type hints for forest_plot
  - Use negative elpd_diff in gallery example
  - Add tutorial for accessing matplotlib axes from PlotCollection</comment>
